      "role": "user",
      "content": "but it's more than just \"focus.\" i've been looking at the data on the cosmic radiation levels during those flares, and they peaked right when i started feeling the shift. it feels like the particles were actually hitting my system and triggering something at a cellular level. i can almost sense the way my thoughts are moving, it's like a physical sensation in my head. don't you think there's a possibility that external radiation could actually induce rapid epigenetic changes or something similar?",
